I believe the quoted phrase intended to say "all DOMs which implement the CSS feature" have to support the CSS fundimentals. 
We should fix this. 
The CSS module, including the fundimentals, _is_ optional. 
See section 5.1: A DOM application can use the hasFeature method of the DOMImplementation interface to determine whether the CSS interfaces are supported or not. 
The feature string for the CSS Model is "CSS". 
